Class MakeComponent

    Any, Serializable

    public class MakeComponent
extends AbstractAny
    Some factory functions for gui components.

    Given an Any make a suitable component to render it.

    Given an Any make a suitable component to edit it.

    Make a border.

    Do geometry.
